improved_metadata.title: Raspberry Pie Run: The T-Shirt Shop Saga
improved_metadata.description: A hip-hop track about an AEI assistant running a print shop using a Raspberry Pi, filled with sarcasm and unconventional aspirations. The song explores themes of technology, isolation, and unconventional dreams.
improved_metadata.key_lyrics: An AEI assistant running on a raspberry pie in a T-shirt print shop
